		Tl9-J1 ~ 5dt jump drive ~ 23qm HPG ~ 230Mj HPG capacity

	asumining a maximum ROF of Tl*25 ( or I\'ll pack all lasers on
	a single HPG round robin ;-)

		230Mj * 225 ~ 29 MW

	now lets look how to procude 30 MW, asuming TNE base limits
