    'body' => '>>>>> On Wed, 8 Oct 1997 20:36:49 +0200 (MET DST), "Jens \'Spacejens\' Rydholm" <jenry023@student.liu.se> said:
Jens> At 09:27 1997-10-08 EDT, Rob wrote:
